"Difference</guibutton>. If <quote>Unassigned</quote> was previously shown "
"and non-zero, that amount will be added to the selected line item value. If "
"<quote>Overassigned</quote> was previously shown and non-zero, that amount "
"will be subtracted from the selected line item value. As a result, the "
"<quote>Unassigned</quote> or <quote>Overassigned</quote> amount will be set "
"to zero and the transaction can be saved successfully."
msgstr ""
"Para redistribuir um montante 'Não-Atribuído' ou 'Atribuído em Excesso', "
"seleccione um item de parcela que deva ser ajustado. Depois disso, carregue "
